    <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; color: #2c3e50; text-decoration: underline;">Vous &ecirc;tes propri&eacute;taire de vos donn&eacute;es et nous respectons &ccedil;a.</span></strong></span></p>
